::: Hell Beast marches through the gasy swamplands accompanied by Marine the 
turtle bot. He took the turtle for two reasons, he was reliable, and he had 
enough firepower to equal two bots. He could not get over this Predacon, but 
most likely it was all to good to be true. :::

::: Marine ::: Commander, the Allience Base is only a few more meters. Shall 
I scout ahead?

::: Megatron, hanging in the back ::: slow down this instant!

::: Hell Beast and Marine ignored his rants :::

::: Hell Beast ::: No, Zardus can be trusted. He is a diplomat.

::: The three entered the Alliences base perimiter and waited to be escourted 
to the ship itself, they didnt want to alarm anyone. :::
